summary:
Here’s a thing about the kiss on the cheek question before things go crazy.
I follow the girl in the gifset on Instagram and...
body:
Here’s a thing about the kiss on the cheek question before things go crazy.

I follow the girl in the gifset on Instagram and she’s one of the most respectful fans I’ve met. I’ve watched the video and read the post she made on this moment and she was super polite and just wanted to ask because she didn’t want to regret not asking. And she completely understood why they said no and was perfectly respectful and the boys were literally fine. She meant nothing by it. She’s one of the fans who actually cares and calls out people on their shitty behavior when it comes to dan and Phil. She asked permission for a pose and was perfectly fine when they said no.

So please don’t crucify someone for something that’s not even an issue.

I just wanted to post this and clear it up so that hopefully it won’t turn into a big thing
